import React from 'react'
import { Box, Button,Container, Grid, Paper, TextField, Typography } from '@mui/material'

export const Login = () => {
  return (
    <Container maxWidth='xl'>
        <Grid
            container direction={'colum'} 
            alignItems={'center'} 
            justifyContent={'center'}
            sx={{minHeight:'100vh'}}
        >
            <Grid item xs={6}>
                <Paper sx={{padding:'1.2em', borderRadius:'0.5em'}}>
                    <Typography variant='h4'>Iniciar Sesión</Typography>
                    <Box component = 'form'>
                        <TextField 
                            fullWidth 
                            label='Email'
                            sx={{mt:2,mb:1.5}}
                            required
                        />
                        <TextField 
                            fullWidth 
                            label='Contraseña'
                            sx={{mt:2,mb:1.5}}
                            required
                        />
                        <Button 
                            type='submit' 
                            fullWidth
                            variant='contained'
                            sx={{mt:2,mb:3}}
                        >
                            Iniciar Sesión
                        </Button>
                    </Box>
                </Paper>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
    </Container>
  )
}
